      "title": "Six year extension for the Governor of the Central Bank",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Governor of the Bank of Ceylon Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe will be appointed as the Governor of the Central Bank for another 06 years with effect from July 04.",
        "The appointment letter was handed over by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to Nandalal Weerasinghe at the President's House."
      ],
